messages.content: Just scouting the area for any potential loot. Can't let any opportunities slip by, you know? And you, Tally? What brings you to Zalesie?

messages.content: It's just a flesh wound, nothing I can't handle. I was in a skirmish earlier but managed to escape with some loot. Speaking of loot, have you seen anything worth checking out around here, Tally?
